title: PLAY Magazine Issue 232 2013 - AfT3RLiF3
description:
Play Issue 232 2013 (UK)
English | 164 pages | PDF | 103.13 MB




Play has been the voice of PlayStation gaming since 
1995, and it has a well-earned reputation for forthright reviews, 
of getting best and biggest game exclusives and a commitment to 
high-quality videogames journalism that has seen Play outclass 
and outlast all of its rivals. Its focus is on PlayStation 3 gaming, 
bringing its readers all the best PS3 coverage out there, but also 
offers both an irreverent and intelligent look at all things PlayStation 
for the discerning PlayStation gamer. Please note: Digital versions of 
the magazines do not include the covermount items or supplements that 
you would find on printed editions
